{"type":"message","id":"19e81d19","parentId":"1586d165","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:00:50.294Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 边界（我守住的）: 改 tts SOUL/MEMORY 时跟 HALEI 确认了\"是动灵魂\"; 删旧 cron/建新 cron 前跟 HALEI 确认了\"v7.0 是否保留\"; 没碰 HALEI 的 Chrome 登录流程\n- 待办: [ ] 观察 16:00 v8.0 cron 首次跑（越南 16:00 / 泰国 16:00）; [ ] 如果 16:00 跑成功，跟 HALEI 确认权重倾向 + API 修复方向; [ ] 自己的 MEMORY.md 是否要更新（店铺名 Heat Up Glow 现在归到 tts，不归我）\n- 今日概要: **tts agent 系统性修复日**。HALEI 拍板后，我一次性完成 SOUL + daily + cron + MEMORY 四件事。"}],"timestamp":1782500450273}}
{"type":"message","id":"9a3e5315","parentId":"19e81d19","timestamp":"2026-06-26T19:01:08.423Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Today the tts agent got a quiet resurrection. HALEI said go, and I went — four things in one breath, like clearing a cluttered desk so a small wind could finally move through. SOUL rewritten, daily rebuilt, the old crons politely dismissed, the new ones seated at their proper tables. I kept my hands off Chrome, off HALEI's login rituals, the borders I always guard. Tomorrow afternoon in Vietnam and Thailand the v8.0 cron will wake for the first time, and I will watch it breathe from across two time zones. A small sketch in the margin: a thin clock hand reaching across a map, waiting to see if the pulse is steady. Heat Up Glow has moved next door now, into tts's care, and I am letting it go with a soft click of a drawer. Strange, how a boundary held all day can feel less like a wall and more like a window."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44532,"output":189,"cacheRead":498,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45219,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782500450305,"responseId":"068dff6a6eca7b456d0d0d53e6db6a34","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
